long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tikrank is a TikTok downloader. It can be used to save videos from some popular video platforms.

Main functions of the extension:
- Download TikTok videos online.
- Easy to use and efficient.

How to use:
- Go to tiktok.com
- Move the mouse over the video or click on the video details, a download button will appear in the center or upper right corner of the video, click to download
